track.name: Run It Up (feat. Offset & Moneybagg Yo)

wiki.summary: “Run It Up“ sees Lil Tjay recruiting both Offset and Moneybagg Yo for a melodic track touching on their individual lifestyles with fame and wealth. The three also detail their extensive array of weaponry and readiness to use it on anyone who may cross paths with them. wiki.content: “Run It Up“ sees Lil Tjay recruiting both Offset and Moneybagg Yo for a melodic track touching on their individual lifestyles with fame and wealth. The three also detail their extensive array of weaponry and readiness to use it on anyone who may cross paths with them. The track was first previewed with a short snippet at the end of the official music video to the Polo G and Fivio Foreign-assisted “Headshot“ on March 22, 2021. Additionally, the track was previewed further in Triller videos in the remaining eleven days before its official release alongside Destined 2 Win on April 2. Read more on Last.fm.
